{"word":"G5506 - χιλίαρχος - chilíarchos - khil-ee'-ar-khos - Captain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χιλίαρχος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chilíarchos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khil-ee'-ar-khos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Captain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரதான மனுஷர், தலைவன், சேனாபதி"},{"paragraph":"colonel, captain, chief, head, the commander of a thousand soldiers"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5507 - χίλιοι - chílioi - khil'-ee-oy/5507\">G5507</a> and <a href=\"#/G757 - ἄρχω - árchō - ar'-kho/757\">G757</a>; the <i>commander of a thousand</i> soldiers (&ldquo;chiliarch&rdquo;), that is, <i>colonel:</i> - (chief, high) captain.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5505/5505\">G5505</a>, <a href=\"#/G5506/5506\">G5506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5507/5507\">G5507</a>"}]}